{"tid":2455206,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"金管局余偉文不認同美國對港官員制裁 對香港金融中心地位仍有信心","createTime":"2021-03-21T01:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T06:09:19.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d6efc6f3ad570d87ce0f2a2ee6d3a1765f5ab2","tid":2455206,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T01:51:03.000Z","msg":"金管局總裁余偉文在本台節目表示，對本港的國際金融中心地位有信心，雖然過去兩年本港經歷很多事，但跨國金融機構仍然覺得本港金融環境穩定，加上本港司法獨立、普通法制度不變，資本市場增長快，相信外資在互聯互通、大灣區、金融科技和綠色金融等方面，會見到機遇，特別是國際內地資金互相流向，香港在門戶角色上具有優勢。 <br />\n<br />\n余偉文表示，不認同美國對部分本港官員作出制裁，強調本港金融系統要自強，金管局會居安思危，做好預案，確保制裁措施不會對金融系統做成影響。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2383909&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfWLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=cde83491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383909</a>"},{"pid":"2eee8bddc3be0a10864d23fdebac702514caa14c","tid":2455206,"uid":284855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T01:54:49.000Z","msg":"一句，執行定唔執行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83503f74b719844c3f1e97e220bc610c66304a46","tid":2455206,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T01:55:18.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊諷刺性說道：『全級第一，明天我們的資產就要回家了。』"},{"pid":"13bb42cbe2896097a4823660360ca1b4344ceb7f","tid":2455206,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T01:56:44.000Z","msg":"中國人對自己中國式民主同人權有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港官員對自己國際金融地位司法法治有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1416edc3f9b04b415be120d9f8b2beb6cf99442b","tid":2455206,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /